kk733e26-5d5d-v4ed-s444-f41f37006d9.title: World of Warcraft
kk733e26-5d5d-v4ed-s444-f41f37006d9.summary: World of Warcraft was inspired by other MMORPG's, particularly EverQuest, with Blizzard setting out to make their own MMORPG and improving on the features of EverQuest. World of Warcraft allows players to create a character avatar and explore an open game world in third- or first-person view, exploring the landscape, fighting various monsters, completing quests, and interacting with non-player characters (NPCs) or other players.
